{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "7ece90b1-7922-433c-b182-cc4d4b1221a3", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7ece90b1-7922-433c-b182-cc4d4b1221a3@1.pkg/1772597613194/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597613665", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7ece90b1-7922-433c-b182-cc4d4b1221a3@1.pkg/1772597613194/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597613665"}, "identifier": "7ece90b1-7922-433c-b182-cc4d4b1221a3", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查集体生活的作用。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：&ldquo;独自完成所有策划&rdquo;没有体现和集体其他同伴共同合作，取得的成长也不是在集体中实现的，因此A选项不符合题意。故A错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：&ldquo;将任务都丢给组员，专注做自己的事&rdquo;是不顾集体，只关注自己的自私做法，是错误的，并没有体现&ldquo;在集体生活中成长&rdquo;，因此B错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：与自己的朋友&ldquo;合作&rdquo;进行作弊的行为违反校规校纪，取得的成绩也是虚假的，并非是真正的进步，故C错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：在英语合作中&ldquo;我&rdquo;的视野不仅变得更加开阔，人际关系也得到了扩宽，可以说实现了成长。因此D正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>因此选D</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）集体生活成就我，让我不断进步。下列选项体现&ldquo;我&rdquo;在集体生活中成长的是（ &nbsp; &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）集体生活成就我，让我不断进步。下列选项体现“我”在集体生活中成长的是（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7ece90b1-7922-433c-b182-cc4d4b1221a3@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977936199", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>作为班级活动组织者，我独自完成所有策划，提高了工作能力</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>参加学习互助小组时，我将任务都丢给组员，专注做自己的事</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>为取得良好期末成绩，我与好朋友互相配合，传递答案来作弊</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>在英语合作学习当中，我的视野变得更开阔，收获到更多朋友</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）集体生活成就我，让我不断进步。下列选项体现&ldquo;我&rdquo;在集体生活中成长的是（ &nbsp; &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source"